reviewText: I have not watch, like the actor.
I am a fan of Antonio Banderas. This was one of his best movies I have ever seen. Worth your time to watch and every penny you'd pay for it.
I wasn't as impressed with this old movie of Antonio Banderas' as I thought I would be.

WARNING!  This DVD features the orignal Spanish language version as well as the English dubbed version.  That is all fine and great, except, with the orignal Spanish version there are no english subtitles?!?  What is the point?

Good quality otherwise.  Too bad.
I thought the movie would be better.  Didn't really make an impression on me.
